Automatically posts GPT-powered test coverage and flaky log summaries to pull requests.

## Features
- Analyzes test coverage (`coverage-summary.json`)
- Summarizes flaky test logs (`logs/test-failures.txt`)
- Posts Markdown-formatted comment to PR
- Optional Slack notifications (via webhook)

## Setup
1. Add these secrets to your repo:
   - `OPENAI_API_KEY`
   - *(optional)* `SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL`
2. Push your test output files:
   - `coverage/coverage-summary.json`
   - `logs/test-failures.txt`

